### Create a page
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "123456789",
  "name": "S-huset",
  "url": "https://facebook.com/shuset",
  "pictureUrl": "https://example.com/logo.jpg",
  "active": true
}

### Create an event
POST http://localhost:8080/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "event-1",
  "pageId": "123456789",
  "title": "Pub Night",
  "description": "Join us for drinks and games!",
  "startTime": "2026-03-20T20:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-03-20T23:00:00",
  "coverImageUrl": "https://example.com/event.jpg",
  "eventURL": "https://facebook.com/event/123"
}

### Get all events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events

### Get future events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events/future